    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently runs roughly, and there are noticeable leaks that need to be addressed before it can be considered reliable for daily use. The exterior shows substantial wear, including several deep scratches, minor dents, and clear coat failure on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing, and several electronic components are non-functional. This is an ideal candidate for a full restoration or as a source for parts.",
